description: This source file defines the main App component for a React-based To-Do list application. It imports necessary dependencies, including React, styles, context provider, and child components such as Header, Footer, ToDoList, and NewToDoForm. The App component composes these components within a ToDoProvider context, establishing the structure of the application's UI with sections for adding, displaying, and filtering to-do items.

methods.name: App()
methods.description: Functional React component that renders the main structure of the To-Do application, wrapping child components within the ToDoProvider context.
